00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:01,558
You're welcome.

641
00:32:01,559 --> 00:32:02,680
I'll get going then.

642
00:32:03,599 --> 00:32:04,599
Thank you.

643
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,480
You're welcome. Try it.

644
00:32:21,519 --> 00:32:22,519
Dr. Lu.

645
00:32:23,119 --> 00:32:25,039
