646
00:32:25,559 --> 00:32:26,559
It's really good.

647
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,759
I'm glad you like it.

648
00:32:28,079 --> 00:32:29,079
I'll cook for you again.

649
00:32:29,559 --> 00:32:31,000
